<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٤٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5261">قَيْسِ بْنِ مُسْلِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2971">طَارِقِ بْنِ شِهَابٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3856">أَبِي مُوسَى </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«قَدِمْتُ عَلَى النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَأَمَرَهُ بِالْحِلِّ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>